Package: bareos-webui-proxy
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - WebUI WebSocket proxy
 Bareos is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides bareos-webui-proxy, a C++ daemon that proxies
 WebSocket connections between the Bareos WebUI and the Bareos Director
 using the CRAM-MD5 authentication protocol.
